# Documentation
docs/site/
# NOTE: CHANGELOG.md, LICENSE.md, GettingStarted/QUICKSTART.md, and the
# notebooks/ contents under docs/src/ are committed symlinks to top-level repo
# files (see docs/build-docs.sh), so they are intentionally not ignored here.
# The notebook symlinks must override the global *.ipynb ignore above.
!docs/src/notebooks/*.ipynb
!docs/src/images/*png
temp*

